data.title: Flat Deli Products
data.text:
Flat Delicatessen Papers are a flat dry waxed paper with full wet strength. They are microwavable. Packaged in an easy dispenser box and Kraft wrapped when size requires. Our Flat Deli products offer a combination of moisture and grease resistant properties perfect with hot foods and demanding performance requirements.

Use for:

Basket liners Scale sheets Sandwich wraps Submarine wraps Hamburger wraps Food prep divider Taco wraps Hot dog or sausage wraps Pizza sheets Portion control divider

We stock a full range of deli paper sizes. Custom sizing or custom printing is also available. For more information call our Customer Service Department at 800-445-4434.
